00:40:23.330 --> 00:40:27.020
I mean, I think that
the challenge with that

00:40:27.020 --> 00:40:30.990
would be if you say you
have a magic bullet,

00:40:30.990 --> 00:40:33.530
then that is exciting
and people buy it.

00:40:33.530 --> 00:40:36.620
Like, they asked me to write
a health column for "Esquire,"

00:40:36.620 --> 00:40:39.140
and I said, all
right, but it's not

00:40:39.140 --> 00:40:40.400
going to be that interesting.

00:40:40.400 --> 00:40:44.010
Because I'm going to write
the same paragraph every week,

00:40:44.010 --> 00:40:47.510
which is, you
know, get exercise,

00:40:47.510 --> 00:40:51.050
eat non-processed foods,
get a lot of sleep.

00:40:51.050 --> 00:40:54.210
